The Zwarte Zaal is a black box of approximately 640m2. Every year, dozens of artistic productions by&nbsp;students and researchers of KASK & Conservatory will be accommodated in this multipurpose room. In addition to try-outs, exhibitions, drama projects&nbsp;and concerts, the Black Hall also hosts conferences and seminars,&nbsp;both internally and externally.

